title: Novos (Os)
body: The first issue of this newspaper appeared on May 1, 1920, and the tenth, which we assume to be the last, in November of the same year. It was edited by students from the Funchal high school and replaced the Gente Nova.

1920: First issue of the newspaper 'Os Novos'
Novembro: Appearance of the tenth issue of the newspaper 'Os Novos'
